---
import { CheckCircle2 } from "@lucide/astro";
---

<section class="features-7">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <h2 class="text-center">Kenapa Banyak Orang Pake Clipcash?</h2>
    
    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <CheckCircle2 class="h-8 w-8 text-green" />
        <div class="feature-content">
          <h3>Karena Pengen Cuan Dari Nge-klip Walaupun Gaptek.</h3>
          <p>Clipcash bikin langkahnya + super simpel. Kamu tinggal ngikutin aja step by step nya.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <CheckCircle2 class="h-8 w-8 text-green" />
        <div class="feature-content">
          <h3>Karena Peluang Monetisasi Ada Buat Yang Upload Konsisten.</h3>
          <p>Ngedit manual butuh waktu 1-3 jam per video, dan kalo gak FYP sama aja gak cuan.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <CheckCircle2 class="h-8 w-8 text-green" />
        <div class="feature-content">
          <h3>Karena Pengen Hasil Klip Yang Cepat Tanpa Perlu Ngedit.</h3>
          <p>Tinggal copy paste link referensi video lalu sistem Clipcash yang bikinin konten nya.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="features-summary text-center">
      <p>Semua dibuat simpel. Semua dijelasin step by step.</p>
      <a href="#pricing" class="btn-primary">🔥 Akses Sekarang - Rp199.000</a>
      <p class="social-proof">2435+ orang udah akses produk ini & mulai raih cuan dari nge-klip!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .features-7 {
    padding: 100px 0;
    background: white;
  }

  .container-narrow {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 900;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  .feature-card {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    background: #fdfdfd;
    padding: 24px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid #eee;
  }

  .text-green { color: #52BD94; flex-shrink: 0; }

  .feature-content h3 {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .feature-content p {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #555;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .features-summary p {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #d32f2f;
    color: white;
    padding: 20px 48px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 20px;
    text-decoration: none;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.2);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .social-proof {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #999 !important;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
